NAME

  KOI8R - Source code filter to escape KOI8-R script

SYNOPSIS

  use KOI8R;

DESCRIPTION

  The KOI8R software provides character oriented Perl scripting
  environment in KOI8-R by easy installation and easy usage.

  - Character oriented regular expression
  - Byte oriented built-in functions
      and
  - Character oriented subroutines
  - Byte oriented regular expression on /b modifier

INSTALLATION

  Just copy KOI8R.pm and Ekoi8r.pm to your @INC directory.
  for example, to C:\Perl\site\lib

SUBROUTINES

  KOI8R::length(charstring)
  KOI8R::substr(charstring, charpos, charlen)
  etc

SEE ALSO

  http://search.cpan.org/~ina/

